# Pre-commit gate for this solo side-project repo.
#
# Runs:
#   1. `tsc -b --noEmit` — full type check on every commit. Fast (~1s
#      incremental) and catches the class of bugs that ESLint can't.
#   2. `lint-staged` — ESLint on staged .ts/.tsx files with --max-warnings 0,
#      so you can't add a new lint warning to a staged file. Existing debt
#      in unstaged parts of the repo stays out of scope, letting the hook
#      stay green until you specifically touch a file with pre-existing
#      warnings.
#
# Bypass with `git commit --no-verify` in an emergency; prefer fixing the
# underlying issue.

npm run typecheck && npx lint-staged
